nh·∫≠n t&amp;agrave;u Nga di chuy·ªÉn xung quanh t&amp;agrave;u chi·∫øn Anh v&amp;agrave; &amp;ocirc;ng &amp;quot;nghe th·∫•y c·∫£ ti·∫øng s&amp;uacute;ng&amp;quot;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ngay sau ƒë&amp;oacute;, B·ªô Qu·ªëc ph&amp;ograve;ng Nga y&amp;ecirc;u c·∫ßu L·∫ßu NƒÉm G&amp;oacute;c v&amp;agrave; ch·ªâ huy l·ª±c l∆∞·ª£ng h·∫£i qu&amp;acirc;n Ho&amp;agrave;ng gia Anh tr&amp;aacute;nh nh·ªØng h&amp;agrave;nh ƒë·ªông g&amp;acirc;y nguy hi·ªÉm t∆∞∆°ng t·ª± ·ªü bi·ªÉn ƒêen.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ph·∫°m Nghƒ©a&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'my-dua-tau-khu-truc-ten-lua-dan-duong-toi-ukraine', './uploads/images/1624883251_ship.jpg', 1, 4, '2021-06-28 19:27:32', '2021-06-28 16:22:36'),
