(11, 4, 3, 'Ng∆∞·ªùi g·ªëc Vi·ªát tranh c·ª≠ t·ªïng th∆∞ k√Ω bang Georgia', '&lt;p&gt;Bee Nguyen, th&amp;agrave;nh vi&amp;ecirc;n ƒë·∫£ng D&amp;acirc;n ch·ªß, tuy&amp;ecirc;n b·ªë c·∫°nh tranh v·ªõi Brad Raffensperger, T·ªïng th∆∞ k&amp;yacute; bang Georgia ƒë∆∞∆°ng nhi·ªám.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Cu·ªôc ƒëua v&amp;agrave;o gh·∫ø t·ªïng th∆∞ k&amp;yacute; bang Georgia tr·ªü n&amp;ecirc;n gay c·∫•n v&amp;agrave;o s&amp;aacute;ng 4/5, khi Bee Nguyen, 39 tu·ªïi, ng∆∞·ªùi M·ªπ g·ªëc Vi·ªát ƒë·∫ßu ti&amp;ecirc;n ƒë∆∞·ª£c b·∫ßu v&amp;agrave;o H·∫° vi·ªán Georgia, tuy&amp;ecirc;n b·ªë gia nh·∫≠p.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;quot;ƒê·∫£ng C·ªông h&amp;ograve;a ƒë&amp;atilde; s·ª≠ d·ª•ng quy·ªÅn h&amp;agrave;nh ƒë·ªÉ b·ªãt mi·ªáng ti·∫øng n&amp;oacute;i c·ªßa c·ª≠ tri, nh·ªØng ng∆∞·ªùi l·ª±a ch·ªçn m·ªôt ng∆∞·ªùi M·ªπ ph·ª•ng s·ª± v&amp;igrave; t·∫•t c·∫£ ch&amp;uacute;ng ta, ch·ª© kh&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;igrave; v&amp;agrave;i ng∆∞·ªùi trong ch&amp;uacute;ng ta&amp;quot;, Bee Nguyen n&amp;oacute;i trong video th&amp;ocirc;ng b&amp;aacute;o tranh c·ª≠. &amp;quot;Nh∆∞ng ch&amp;uacute;ng ta s·∫Ω kh&amp;ocirc;ng cho ph&amp;eacute;p b·∫•t k·ª≥ ai c·∫£n tr·ªü quy·ªÅn ƒë∆∞·ª£c ti·∫øn t·ªõi con ƒë∆∞·ªùng d&amp;acirc;n ch·ªß t·ª± do v&amp;agrave; c&amp;ocirc;ng b·∫±ng&amp;quot;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Bee Nguyen&quot; src=&quot;https://i1-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2021/05/05/f0f9061e61eb993cd96cbb8fd6b45e-6414-5165-1620189017.jpg?w=680&amp;amp;h=0&amp;amp;q=100&amp;amp;dpr=1&amp;amp;fit=crop&amp;amp;s=fQ-V-AUyFsaWAr50jaFrKA&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;Bee Nguyen trong m·ªôt cu·ªôc tu·∫ßn h&amp;agrave;nh ph·∫£n ƒë·ªëi th&amp;ugrave; gh&amp;eacute;t ng∆∞·ªùi g·ªëc &amp;Aacute; t·∫°i Atlanta h·ªìi th&amp;aacute;ng 3. ·∫¢nh:&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Reuters&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Raffensperger, th&amp;agrave;nh vi&amp;ecir