(12, 1, 20, 'Harrison Ford b·ªã th∆∞∆°ng khi quay \"Indiana Jones 5\"', '&lt;p&gt;T&amp;agrave;i t·ª≠ Harrison Ford g·∫∑p ch·∫•n th∆∞∆°ng ·ªü vai tr&amp;ecirc;n phim tr∆∞·ªùng &amp;quot;Indiana Jones 5&amp;quot; v&amp;agrave; s·∫Ω ph·∫£i ngh·ªâ ng∆°i m·ªôt th·ªùi gian.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ng&amp;agrave;y 23/6, ngu·ªìn tin c·ªßa&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Variety&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;cho bi·∫øt: &amp;quot;Trong m·ªôt bu·ªïi t·∫≠p c·∫£nh chi·∫øn ƒë·∫•u, Harrison Ford d&amp;iacute;nh ch·∫•n th∆∞∆°ng ·ªü vai. C&amp;ocirc;ng vi·ªác s·∫£n xu·∫•t phim v·∫´n di·ªÖn ra song song qu&amp;aacute; tr&amp;igrave;nh ƒëi·ªÅu tr·ªã. Trong v&amp;agrave;i tu·∫ßn t·ªõi, &amp;ecirc;-k&amp;iacute;p s·∫Ω ƒëi·ªÅu ch·ªânh l·ªãch quay ƒë·ªÉ th·ª±c hi·ªán c&amp;aacute;c c·∫£nh kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; Ford tham gia tr∆∞·ªõc&amp;quot;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Harrison Ford trong vai Indiana Jones&quot; src=&quot;https://i1-giaitri.vnecdn.net/2021/06/24/Indiana-Jones-4165-1624529188.jpg?w=680&amp;amp;h=0&amp;amp;q=100&amp;amp;dpr=1&amp;amp;fit=crop&amp;amp;s=xu2ALS-0ro_p8bl8IvmPNQ&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;Harrison Ford trong vai Indiana Jones. ·∫¢nh:&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Disney&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;ƒêo&amp;agrave;n phim kh&amp;ocirc;ng ti·∫øt l·ªô m·ª©c ƒë·ªô nghi&amp;ecirc;m tr·ªçng c·ªßa v·∫øt th∆∞∆°ng. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, Ford d·ª± ki·∫øn ph·∫£i ngh·ªâ v&amp;agrave;i tu·∫ßn. Nam di·ªÖn vi&amp;ecirc;n nhi·ªÅu l·∫ßn g·∫∑p tai n·∫°n trong s·ª± nghi·ªáp ƒë&amp;oacute;ng phim h&amp;agrave;nh ƒë·ªông. ƒê·∫ßu th·∫≠p ni&amp;ecirc;n 1980, Ford b·ªã th∆∞∆°ng n·∫∑ng ·ªü l∆∞ng khi quay&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Indiana Jones and The Temple of Doom&lt;/em&gt;. &amp;Ocirc;ng c≈©ng b·ªã ch·∫•n th∆∞∆°ng ch&amp;acirc;n khi ƒë&amp;oacute;ng&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;Star Wars: The Force Awakens&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;(2015).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&