(21, 7, 3, 'S·ªë ca m·∫Øc Covid-19 ·ªü ch√¢u Phi tƒÉng m·∫°nh, Nga ghi nh·∫≠n k·ª∑ l·ª•c ƒëau ƒë·ªõn v√¨ ƒë·∫°i d·ªãch', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GD&amp;amp;Tƒê - Theo Worldometer, th·∫ø gi·ªõi c&amp;oacute; 182.176.458 ca m·∫Øc Covid-19, g·ªìm 309.730 ca m·ªõi. S·ªë ca t·ª≠ vong l&amp;agrave; 3.944.936 ca, g·ªìm 5.792 ca m·ªõi.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://images.giaoducthoidai.vn/public/yench/2021-06-29/covid.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:399px; width:600px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trung t&amp;acirc;m Ki·ªÉm so&amp;aacute;t v&amp;agrave; Ph&amp;ograve;ng ng·ª´a D·ªãch b·ªánh&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;ch&amp;acirc;u Phi&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;(CDC ch&amp;acirc;u Phi) cho bi·∫øt, t&amp;iacute;nh ƒë·∫øn tr∆∞a ng&amp;agrave;y 28/6 s·ªë ca m·∫Øc Covid-19 ƒë∆∞·ª£c x&amp;aacute;c nh·∫≠n ·ªü ch&amp;acirc;u l·ª•c n&amp;agrave;y ƒë&amp;atilde; l&amp;ecirc;n t·ªõi 5.417.858. CDC ch&amp;acirc;u Phi l&amp;agrave; c∆° quan chƒÉm s&amp;oacute;c s·ª©c kh·ªèe chuy&amp;ecirc;n bi·ªát c·ªßa Li&amp;ecirc;n minh ch&amp;acirc;u Phi g·ªìm 55 th&amp;agrave;nh vi&amp;ecirc;n. H·ªç cho bi·∫øt t·ªïng s·ªë ng∆∞·ªùi ch·∫øt v&amp;igrave; ƒë·∫°i d·ªãch t·∫°i ƒë&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; 141.290 ng∆∞·ªùi, trong khi ƒë&amp;oacute; 4.750.166 ca ƒë&amp;atilde; kh·ªèi b·ªánh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nam Phi, Maroc, Tunisia, Ethiopia v&amp;agrave; Ai C·∫≠p l&amp;agrave; nh·ªØng qu·ªëc gia c&amp;oacute; nhi·ªÅu ca b·ªánh nh·∫•t ch&amp;acirc;u l·ª•c. Nam Phi c&amp;oacute; s·ªë ca m·∫Øc cao nh·∫•t ch&amp;acirc;u Phi v·ªõi 1.928.897 ca, trong khi Morocco b&amp;aacute;o c&amp;aacute;o 529.676 ca v&amp;agrave;o tr∆∞a h&amp;ocirc;m qua.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Mi·ªÅn nam ch&amp;acirc;u Phi l&amp;agrave; khu v·ª±c b·ªã ·∫£nh h∆∞·ªüng nhi·ªÅu nh·∫•t, ti·∫øp theo l&amp;agrave; ph&amp;iacute;a b·∫Øc v&amp;agrave; ph&amp;iacute;a ƒë&amp;ocirc;ng. Trong khi ƒë&amp;oacute;, Trung Phi