(22, 7, 3, 'M·ªπ v√† Ukraine t·∫≠p tr·∫≠n h·∫£i qu√¢n th∆∞·ªùng ni√™n tr√™n Bi·ªÉn ƒêen', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;T∆∞ l·ªánh h·∫£i qu&amp;acirc;n Ukraine Oleksiy Neizhpapa cho bi·∫øt cu·ªôc t·∫≠p tr·∫≠n nh·∫±m ph&amp;aacute;t ƒëi th&amp;ocirc;ng ƒëi·ªáp v·ªÅ duy tr&amp;igrave; s·ª± ·ªïn ƒë·ªãnh v&amp;agrave; h&amp;ograve;a b&amp;igrave;nh trong khu v·ª±c.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://cdnimg.vietnamplus.vn/uploaded/pcfo/2021_06_29/ttxvn_2906_bien_den.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;My va Ukraine tap tran hai quan thuong nien tren Bien Den hinh anh 1&quot; src=&quot;https://cdnimg.vietnamplus.vn/t620/uploaded/pcfo/2021_06_29/ttxvn_2906_bien_den.jpg&quot; title=&quot;M·ªπ v&agrave; Ukraine t·∫≠p tr·∫≠n h·∫£i qu&acirc;n th∆∞·ªùng ni&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n Bi·ªÉn ƒêen h&igrave;nh ·∫£nh 1&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12px&quot;&gt;T&amp;agrave;u khu tr·ª•c trang b·ªã t&amp;ecirc;n l·ª≠a d·∫´n ƒë∆∞·ªùng c·ªßa M·ªπ USS Ross. (·∫¢nh: AFP/TTXVN)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ng&amp;agrave;y 28/6, M·ªπ v&amp;agrave; Ukraine ƒë&amp;atilde; b·∫Øt ƒë·∫ßu cu·ªôc&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.vietnamplus.vn/tags/t%e1%ba%adp-tr%e1%ba%adn-h%e1%ba%a3i-qu%c3%a2n.vnp&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;t·∫≠p tr·∫≠n h·∫£i qu&amp;acirc;n&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;ƒëa ph∆∞∆°ng th∆∞·ªùng ni&amp;ecirc;n Sea Breeze (Gi&amp;oacute; bi·ªÉn) 2021 t·∫°i Bi·ªÉn ƒêen.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ph&amp;aacute;t bi·ªÉu trong l·ªÖ khai m·∫°c t·∫°i th&amp;agrave;nh ph·ªë Odessa (Ukraine), T∆∞ l·ªánh h·∫£i qu&amp;acirc;n Ukraine Oleksiy Neizhpapa cho bi·∫øt cu·ªôc t·∫≠p tr·∫≠n nh·∫±m ph&amp;aacute;t ƒëi th&amp;ocirc;ng ƒëi·ªáp v·ªÅ duy tr&amp;igrave; s·ª± ·ªïn ƒë·ªãnh v&amp;agrave; h&amp;ograve;a b&amp;igrave;nh trong khu v·ª±c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;c cu·ªôc t·∫≠p tr·∫≠n Sea Breeze ƒë&amp;atilde; di·ªÖn ra 21 l·∫ßn k·ªÉ t·ª´ nƒÉm 1997. NƒÉm nay, cu·ªôc t·∫≠p tr·∫≠n d·ª± ki·∫øn k&amp;eacute;o d&amp;agrave;i trong 2 tu·∫ßn v·ªõi s·ª± tham gia c·ªßa kho·∫£ng 5.000 qu&amp;acirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n t·ª´ 32 qu·ªëc gia c&amp;ugrave;ng 32 t&amp;agrave;u, bao g·ªìm c·∫£ t&amp;agrave;u khu tr·ª•c t&amp;ecirc;n l·ª≠a d·∫´n ƒë∆∞·ªùng USS Ross c·ªßa L·ª±c l∆∞·ª£ng&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.vietnamplus.vn/tags/H%e1%ba%a3i-qu%c3%a2n-M%e1%bb%b9.vnp&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;H·∫£i qu&amp;acirc;n M·ªπ&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;·ªü ƒê·ªãa Trung H·∫£i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Cu·ªôc t·∫≠p tr·∫≠n di·ªÖn ra v&amp;agrave;i ng&amp;agrave;y sau khi x·∫£y ra tranh c&amp;atilde;i xung quanh vi·ªác t&amp;agrave;u khu tr·ª•c HMS Defender c·ªßa Anh ƒëi v&amp;agrave;o h·∫£i ph·∫≠n c·ªßa Nga ·ªü Bi·ªÉn ƒêen.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ph&amp;iacute;a Nga cho r·∫±ng t&amp;agrave;u HMS Defender c·ªßa Anh ƒë&amp;atilde; ti·∫øn s&amp;acirc;u v&amp;agrave;o v&amp;ugrave;ng bi·ªÉn c·ªßa Nga 3km ·ªü khu v·ª±c m≈©i Fiolent thu·ªôc B&amp;aacute;n ƒë·∫£o Crimea ng&amp;agrave;y 23/6, bu·ªôc t&amp;agrave;u tu·∫ßn tra c·ªßa Nga ph·∫£i b·∫Øn c·∫£nh c&amp;aacute;o.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo ng∆∞·ªùi ph&amp;aacute;t ng&amp;ocirc;n ƒêi·ªán Kremlin &amp;ocirc;ng Dmitry Peskov, ƒë·ªông th&amp;aacute;i tr&amp;ecirc;n c·ªßa t&amp;agrave;u khu tr·ª•c Anh l&amp;agrave; &amp;quot;h&amp;agrave;nh ƒë·ªông khi&amp;ecirc;u kh&amp;iacute;ch&amp;quot; v&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&amp;ugrave; h·ª£p v·ªõi lu·∫≠t ph&amp;aacute;p qu·ªëc t·∫ø.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, B·ªô Qu·ªëc ph&amp;ograve;ng Anh ƒë&amp;atilde; b&amp;aacute;c b·ªè th&amp;ocirc;ng tin do ph&amp;iacute;a Nga ƒë∆∞a ra, kh·∫≥ng ƒë·ªãnh kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; ph&amp;aacute;t s&amp;uacute;ng c·∫£nh c&amp;aacute;o n&amp;agrave;o nh·∫±m v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;agrave;u HMS Defender, ƒë·ªìng th·ªùi nh·∫•n m·∫°nh r·∫±ng t&amp;agrave;u n&amp;agrave;y ƒë∆°n thu·∫ßn ch·ªâ th·ª±c hi·ªán h·∫£i tr&amp;igrave;nh nh∆∞ th∆∞·ªùng l·ªá t·ª´ Odessa (&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.vietnamplus.vn/tags/Ukraine.vnp&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ukraine&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) ƒë·∫øn Gruzia qua Bi·ªÉn ƒêen v&amp;agrave; ƒë&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; tuy·∫øn ƒë∆∞·ªùng ƒë∆∞·ª£c lu·∫≠t ph&amp;aacute;p qu·ªëc t·∫ø cho ph&amp;eacute;p.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Sau v·ª• vi·ªác, ng&amp;agrave;y 26/6, Trung t&amp;acirc;m Ch·ªâ huy Qu·ªëc ph&amp;ograve;ng thu·ªôc B·ªô Qu·ªëc ph&amp;ograve;ng Nga cho bi·∫øt c&amp;aacute;c l·ª±c l∆∞·ª£ng thu·ªôc H·∫°m ƒë·ªôi Bi·ªÉn ƒêen c·ªßa n∆∞·ªõc n&amp;agrave;y ƒëang gi&amp;aacute;m s&amp;aacute;t di chuy·ªÉn c·ªßa t&amp;agrave;u khu tr·ª•c trang b·ªã t&amp;ecirc;n l·ª≠a d·∫´n ƒë∆∞·ªùng c·ªßa M·ªπ USS Ross v&amp;agrave;o Bi·ªÉn ƒêen ƒë·ªÉ tham gia cu·ªôc t·∫≠p tr·∫≠n Sea Breeze.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B·ªô Qu·ªëc ph&amp;ograve;ng Nga ƒë&amp;atilde; k&amp;ecirc;u g·ªçi L·∫ßu NƒÉm G&amp;oacute;c, c≈©ng nh∆∞ B·ªô ch·ªâ huy h·∫£i qu&amp;acirc;n Anh, &amp;quot;th·ª±c hi·ªán &amp;yacute; th·ª©c chung&amp;quot; khi ph&amp;aacute;i t&amp;agrave;u ƒë·∫øn&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.vietnamplus.vn/tags/Bi%e1%bb%83n-%c4%90en.vnp&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bi·ªÉn ƒêen&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;./.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;T·∫•t ƒê·∫°t (TTXVN/Vietnam+)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'my-va-ukraine-tap-tran-hai-quan-thuong-nien-tren-bien-en', './uploads/images/1624930403_ttxvn_2906_bien_den.jpg', 1, 18, '2021-06-29 08:33:23', '2021-07-07 07:02:59'),
