Å cao, sinh vi&amp;ecirc;n n∆∞·ªõc ngo&amp;agrave;i... ƒëi/ƒë·∫øn Vi·ªát Nam.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, C·ª•c H&amp;agrave;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng Vi·ªát Nam&amp;nbsp;c≈©ng ƒë∆∞a ra d·ª± b&amp;aacute;o t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh nƒÉm 2021 s·∫Ω c·∫£i thi·ªán so v·ªõi nƒÉm 2020, ƒë·∫∑c bi·ªát v&amp;agrave;o n·ª≠a cu·ªëi nƒÉm 2021 khi vi·ªác ti&amp;ecirc;m v·∫Øc xin ph&amp;ograve;ng Covid-19 ƒë∆∞·ª£c ƒë·∫©y nhanh t·∫°i Vi·ªát Nam&amp;nbsp;v&amp;agrave;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://thanhnien.vn/the-gioi/&quot; rel=&quot;&quot;&gt;th·∫ø gi·ªõi&lt;/a&gt;. ƒê·∫∑c bi·ªát, t·∫°i nhi·ªÅu th·ªã tr∆∞·ªùng tr·ªçng ƒëi·ªÉm nh∆∞ ƒê&amp;ocirc;ng B·∫Øc &amp;Aacute;, ch&amp;acirc;u &amp;Acirc;u s·∫Ω ƒë·ªß ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán t·∫°o mi·ªÖn d·ªãch c·ªông ƒë·ªìng, l&amp;agrave;m c∆° s·ªü t·ª´ng b∆∞·ªõc m·ªü l·∫°i th·ªã tr∆∞·ªùng qu·ªëc t·∫ø qu&amp;yacute; 3, ƒë·∫ßu qu&amp;yacute; 4 nƒÉm nay. D·ª± b&amp;aacute;o th·ªã tr∆∞·ªùng h&amp;agrave;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng Vi·ªát Nam&amp;nbsp;s·∫Ω b·∫Øt ƒë·∫ßu ph·ª•c h·ªìi t·ª´ gi·ªØa qu&amp;yacute; 3/2021 v·ªõi s·∫£n l∆∞·ª£ng th&amp;ocirc;ng qua c&amp;aacute;c c·∫£ng h&amp;agrave;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng nƒÉm 2021 ∆∞·ªõc ƒë·∫°t tr&amp;ecirc;n 70 tri·ªáu l∆∞·ª£t h&amp;agrave;nh kh&amp;aacute;ch.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mai H&amp;agrave;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;ƒê&amp;aacute;ng l∆∞u &amp;yacute;, vi·ªác &amp;ldquo;b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute;&amp;rdquo; v&amp;eacute; m&amp;aacute;y bay trong b·ªëi c·∫£nh c&amp;aacute;c h&amp;atilde;ng h&amp;agrave;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng ƒëang g·∫∑p &amp;aacute;p l·ª±c l·ªõn v·ªÅ t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh ho&amp;agrave;n to&amp;agrave;n c&amp;oacute; th·ªÉ g&amp;acirc;y ra s·ª± s·ª•t gi·∫£m doanh thu tr·∫ßm tr·ªçng, m&amp;agrave; t·ªìi t·ªá h∆°n l&amp;agrave; ƒë·∫©y h&amp;atilde;ng h&amp;agrave;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;igrave;nh tr·∫°ng ph&amp;aacute; s·∫£n, khi doanh thu kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&amp;ugrave; ƒë·∫Øp n·ªïi c&amp;aacute;c chi ph&amp;i