;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Covid-19 c&amp;ograve;n g&amp;acirc;y nhi·ªÅu th&amp;aacute;ch th·ª©c cho c·∫£ c·ªông ƒë·ªìng, nh∆∞ng tinh th·∫ßn ƒëo&amp;agrave;n k·∫øt v&amp;agrave; nh·ªØng ƒë&amp;oacute;ng g&amp;oacute;p thi·∫øt th·ª±c v&amp;agrave; &amp;yacute; nghƒ©a nh∆∞ th·∫ø n&amp;agrave;y s·∫Ω l&amp;agrave; ƒë·ªông l·ª±c to l·ªõn ƒë·ªÉ to&amp;agrave;n x&amp;atilde; h·ªôi s·ªõm v∆∞·ª£t qua ƒë·∫°i d·ªãch.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;blockquote&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;SCGP l&amp;agrave; nh&amp;agrave; cung c·∫•p gi·∫£i ph&amp;aacute;p bao b&amp;igrave; to&amp;agrave;n di·ªán h&amp;agrave;ng ƒë·∫ßu t·∫°i ASEAN v&amp;agrave; l&amp;agrave; nh&amp;agrave; s·∫£n xu·∫•t gi·∫•y bao b&amp;igrave; v&amp;agrave; bao b&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c-t&amp;ocirc;ng g·ª£n s&amp;oacute;ng l·ªõn nh·∫•t ASEAN (theo gi·∫£i th∆∞·ªüng Frost &amp;amp; Sullivan, 2019). C&amp;aacute;c s·∫£n ph·∫©m c·ªßa SCGP bao g·ªìm Bao b&amp;igrave; Gi·∫•y, Bao b&amp;igrave; Nh·ª±a (PPP), Bao b&amp;igrave; Th·ª±c ph·∫©m, Thi·∫øt k·∫ø, In ·∫•n v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c gi·∫£i ph&amp;aacute;p ƒëa d·∫°ng kh&amp;aacute;c ƒë·ªÉ ƒë&amp;aacute;p ·ª©ng nhu c·∫ßu c·ªßa kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng. C&amp;ocirc;ng ty C·ªï ph·∫ßn Bao b&amp;igrave; Bi&amp;ecirc;n H&amp;ograve;a (SOVI) l&amp;agrave; c&amp;ocirc;ng ty th&amp;agrave;nh vi&amp;ecirc;n c·ªßa SCGP t·∫°i Vi·ªát Nam, chuy&amp;ecirc;n s·∫£n xu·∫•t v&amp;agrave; kinh doanh bao b&amp;igrave; gi·∫•y (g·ªìm bao b&amp;igrave; carton v&amp;agrave; bao b&amp;igrave; offset) v·ªõi th∆∞∆°ng hi·ªáu SOVI.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;(*)Ngu·ªìn:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://hcdc.vn/category/thong-tin/huong-dan-cach-ly-xet-nghiem-nguoi-den-tu-cac-dia-phuong-khac-ve-tp/danh-sach-cac-diem-phong-toa-tai-tpho-chi-minh-cap-nhat-luc-10-gio-ngay-0572021-abf899ccda8a3757c6ddf6542e317919.html&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://hcdc.vn/category/thong-tin/huong-dan-cach-ly-xet-nghiem-nguoi-den-tu-cac-dia-phuong-khac-ve-tp/danh-sach-cac-diem-phong-