nh (69 tu·ªïi, ng·ª• Q.T&amp;acirc;n Ph&amp;uacute;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://thanhnien.vn/doi-song/mac-ket-giua-sai-gon-thoi-covid-19-tho-anh-ngay-buu-dien-tp-cay-dang-rao-ban-xe-dream-1407205.html&quot; rel=&quot;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;TP.HCM&lt;/a&gt;) ƒë&amp;atilde; t&amp;acirc;m s·ª± r·∫±ng cu·ªôc ƒë·ªùi c·ªßa v·ª£ ch·ªìng ƒë&amp;atilde; thay ƒë·ªïi ho&amp;agrave;n to&amp;agrave;n, sang m·ªôt trang m·ªõi t∆∞∆°i s&amp;aacute;ng h∆°n. &amp;Ocirc;ng mu·ªën g·ª≠i l·ªùi c·∫£m ∆°n ƒë·∫øn B&amp;aacute;o&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Thanh Ni&amp;ecirc;n&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;v&amp;agrave; nh·ªØng m·∫°nh th∆∞·ªùng qu&amp;acirc;n ƒë&amp;atilde; gi&amp;uacute;p ƒë·ª°, ·ªßng h·ªô m&amp;igrave;nh trong nh·ªØng ng&amp;agrave;y qua.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h2&gt;&amp;ldquo;T·ª´ nay t&amp;ocirc;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;ograve;n ph·∫£i ƒÉn xin&amp;rdquo;&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&amp;acirc;m s·ª± v·ªõi PV, &amp;ocirc;ng Vinh khi th&amp;igrave; kh&amp;oacute;c v&amp;igrave; x&amp;uacute;c ƒë·ªông, khi th&amp;igrave; l·∫°i c∆∞·ªùi v&amp;igrave; nh·ªØng ng&amp;agrave;y qua nh·∫≠n ƒë∆∞·ª£c qu&amp;aacute; nhi·ªÅu ni·ªÅm vui m&amp;agrave; c·∫£ cu·ªôc ƒë·ªùi &amp;ocirc;ng ch∆∞a bao gi·ªù c&amp;oacute;. &amp;Ocirc;ng n&amp;oacute;i b&amp;acirc;y gi·ªù &amp;ocirc;ng &amp;ldquo;kh·ªèe r·ªìi, ƒë·ªß ti·ªÅn xoay x·ªü r·ªìi, t·ª´ nay kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;ograve;n ph·∫£i ƒëi ƒÉn xin n·ªØa&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Vinh k·ªÉ ngay sau khi b&amp;agrave;i vi·∫øt ƒë∆∞·ª£c ƒëƒÉng t·∫£i v&amp;agrave;o tr∆∞a 3.7, ch·ªâ trong bu·ªïi chi·ªÅu h&amp;ocirc;m ƒë&amp;oacute; ƒë&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; r·∫•t nhi·ªÅu ng∆∞·ªùi ƒë·∫øn t·∫∑ng qu&amp;agrave;, n&amp;agrave;o l&amp;agrave; b&amp;aacute;nh tr&amp;aacute;i, rau c·ªß qu·∫£, n&amp;agrave;o l&amp;agrave; ti·ªÅn m·∫∑t khi·∫øn &amp;ocirc;ng ch·ªü v·ªÅ kh&amp;ocirc;ng n·ªïi.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;ƒê·∫øn ng&amp;agrave;y h&amp;ocirc;m sau, &amp;ocirc;ng qu&amp;aacute; b·∫•t ng·ªù v&amp;igrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng th·ªÉ ƒ