 c·ª• b&amp;agrave; n&amp;agrave;y n&amp;oacute;i: &amp;ldquo;T&amp;ocirc;i kh&amp;oacute;, anh c≈©ng kh&amp;oacute;, th&amp;ocirc;i m&amp;igrave;nh gi&amp;uacute;p nhau qua l&amp;uacute;c n&amp;agrave;y. Anh kh&amp;oacute; h∆°n t&amp;ocirc;i anh m·ªõi ƒëi xin, anh nh·∫≠n cho t&amp;ocirc;i vui&amp;rdquo; khi·∫øn &amp;ocirc;ng Vinh x&amp;uacute;c ƒë·ªông.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ng&amp;agrave;y nh·∫≠n ƒë∆∞·ª£c cu·ªôc g·ªçi v&amp;agrave; s·ª± gi&amp;uacute;p ƒë·ª° c·ªßa ch·ªã Nguy·ªÖn ƒê·ªó Tr&amp;uacute;c Ph∆∞∆°ng (25 tu·ªïi), &amp;ocirc;ng Vinh n&amp;oacute;i ƒë&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; ng&amp;agrave;y thay ƒë·ªïi to&amp;agrave;n b·ªô cu·ªôc ƒë·ªùi m&amp;igrave;nh. S·ªë ti·ªÅn 150 tri·ªáu ƒë·ªìng ƒë∆∞·ª£c ch·ªã Tr&amp;uacute;c Ph∆∞∆°ng quy&amp;ecirc;n g&amp;oacute;p ƒë∆∞·ª£c ƒë&amp;atilde; khi·∫øn &amp;ocirc;ng Vinh v&amp;agrave; v·ª£ v·ª° &amp;ograve;a.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;table align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;B&aacute;c b·∫£o v·ªá ƒÉn xin gi·ªØa d·ªãch Covid-19: &lsquo;C·∫£m ∆°n s·ª± t·ª≠ t·∫ø c·ªßa ng∆∞·ªùi S&agrave;i G&ograve;n&rsquo; - ·∫£nh 2&quot; src=&quot;https://image.thanhnien.vn/2048/uploaded/thanhthuy/2021_07_06/anh3_rtgl.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:353px; width:500px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;Nh·∫≠n ƒë∆∞·ª£c s·ª± gi&amp;uacute;p ƒë·ª° c·ªßa c·ªông ƒë·ªìng, &amp;ocirc;ng vui m·ª´ng n&amp;oacute;i &amp;ldquo;t·ª´ nay m&amp;igrave;nh kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;ograve;n ph·∫£i ƒëi xin n·ªØa&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;·∫¢NH: CAO AN BI&amp;Ecirc;N&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng ti·∫øp l·ªùi: &amp;ldquo;T&amp;ocirc;i th·ª±c s·ª± bi·∫øt ∆°n c&amp;ocirc; Ph∆∞∆°ng, c&amp;ocirc; l&amp;agrave; m·ªôt ng∆∞·ªùi t·ª≠ t·∫ø. Kh&amp;ocirc;ng ch·ªâ d·∫´n t&amp;ocirc;i ra ng&amp;a