khƒÉn kh&amp;aacute;c c≈©ng s·∫Ω c&amp;oacute; ph·∫ßn c·ªßa h·ªç, b&amp;aacute;c ƒë·ª´ng lo&amp;rdquo; l&amp;agrave;m cho &amp;ocirc;ng Vinh th·∫•y ·∫•m l&amp;ograve;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;S&amp;aacute;ng 6.7, &amp;ocirc;ng Vinh cho bi·∫øt &amp;ocirc;ng ƒë&amp;atilde; ·ªßng h·ªô h∆°n 50kg g·∫°o ƒë∆∞·ª£c m·∫°nh th∆∞·ªùng qu&amp;acirc;n t·∫∑ng cho P.T&amp;acirc;n S∆°n Nh&amp;igrave; (Q.T&amp;acirc;n Ph&amp;uacute;) ƒë·ªÉ h·ªó tr·ª£ cho nh·ªØng ng∆∞·ªùi ƒëang s·ªëng trong khu c&amp;aacute;ch ly, phong t·ªèa. Ri&amp;ecirc;ng v·ªÅ s·ªë ti·ªÅn l·ªõn trong s·ªï ti·∫øt ki·ªám, &amp;ocirc;ng n&amp;oacute;i m&amp;igrave;nh s·∫Ω d&amp;ugrave;ng n&amp;oacute; ƒë·ªÉ d∆∞·ª°ng gi&amp;agrave; ho·∫∑c xoay x·ªü khi c&amp;oacute; vi·ªác th·ª±c s·ª± c·∫ßn thi·∫øt.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i h·ªèi &amp;ldquo;H·∫øt d·ªãch, ch&amp;uacute; ƒë·ªãnh l&amp;agrave;m g&amp;igrave;?&amp;rdquo;, &amp;ocirc;ng Vinh c∆∞·ªùi r·ªìi n&amp;oacute;i: &amp;ldquo;C&amp;oacute; m·ªôt m·∫°nh th∆∞·ªùng qu&amp;acirc;n g·ªçi cho t&amp;ocirc;i, n&amp;oacute;i h·ªç c&amp;oacute; m·ªôt m·∫£nh v∆∞·ªùn l·ªõn ·ªü S&amp;agrave;i G&amp;ograve;n c·∫ßn ng∆∞·ªùi chƒÉm s&amp;oacute;c. N·∫øu ƒë∆∞·ª£c v·ª£ ch·ªìng t&amp;ocirc;i c&amp;oacute; th·ªÉ ƒë·∫øn ·ªü, chƒÉm s&amp;oacute;c v∆∞·ªùn r·ªìi h·∫±ng th&amp;aacute;ng ƒë∆∞·ª£c nh·∫≠n ti·ªÅn l∆∞∆°ng. Tu·ªïi gi&amp;agrave; v·ªÅ tr·ªìng c&amp;acirc;y tr·ªìng rau c≈©ng vui l·∫Øm&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&amp;agrave; T∆∞∆°ng (v·ª£ &amp;ocirc;ng Vinh) khi hay tin ch·ªìng ƒëi xin th&amp;igrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng gi·∫•u ƒë∆∞·ª£c b·∫•t ng·ªù. &amp;ldquo;T&amp;ocirc;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng bi·∫øt &amp;ocirc;ng ·∫•y l&amp;agrave;m v·∫≠y, ch·ª© bi·∫øt c·ª° n&amp;agrave;o c·ª° t&amp;ocirc;i c≈©ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng cho&amp;hellip;&amp;rdquo;. Nghe v·ª£ t&amp;acirc;m s·ª±, &amp;ocirc;ng Vinh n&amp;oacute;i vui: &amp;ldquo;Nh∆∞ng nh·ªù v·∫≠y m&amp;agrave; v·ª£ ch·ªìng m&amp;igrave;nh qua ƒë∆∞·ª£c kh&amp;oacute; khƒÉn ƒë&amp;uacute;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&amp;agrave;&amp;rdquo;. Hai v·ª£ ch·ªìng ƒë·ªÅu c∆∞·ªùi&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;table align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;B&aacute;c b·∫£o v·ªá ƒÉn xin gi·ªØa d·ªãch Covid-19: &lsquo;C·∫£m ∆°n s·ª± t·ª≠ t·∫ø c·ªßa ng∆∞·ªùi S&agrave;i G&ograve;n&rsquo; - ·∫£nh 3&quot; src=&quot;https://image.thanhnien.vn/2048/uploaded/thanhthuy/2021_07_06/anh4_ygqy.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:353px; width:500px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;V·ª£ ch·ªìng &amp;ocirc;ng Vinh ƒë·ªÅu kh&amp;ocirc;ng gi·∫•u ƒë∆∞·ª£c ni·ªÅm vui v&amp;igrave; nh·ªØng ng&amp;agrave;y qua nh·∫≠n ƒë∆∞·ª£c s·ª± quan t&amp;acirc;m, y&amp;ecirc;u th∆∞∆°ng c·ªßa qu&amp;aacute; nhi·ªÅu ng∆∞·ªùi&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;·∫¢NH: CAO AN BI&amp;Ecirc;N&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong cƒÉn tr·ªç nh·ªè ƒë&amp;atilde; t·ª´ r·∫•t l&amp;acirc;u ng·ª•p l·∫∑n trong n·ªói lo &amp;ldquo;c∆°m, &amp;aacute;o, g·∫°o, ti·ªÅn&amp;rdquo;, nay b·ªóng b·ª´ng s&amp;aacute;ng h·∫≥n b·ªüi ti·∫øng c∆∞·ªùi. T·∫•t c·∫£ ƒë·ªÅu nh·ªù s·ª± t·ª≠ t·∫ø &amp;ldquo;qu&amp;aacute; m·ª©c&amp;rdquo; c·ªßa ng∆∞·ªùi S&amp;agrave;i G&amp;ograve;n v·ªën t·ª´ b·∫•y l&amp;acirc;u nay v·∫´n v·∫≠y&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Chia s·∫ª v·ªõi PV&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;Thanh Ni&amp;ecirc;n&lt;/em&gt;, ch·ªã Nguy·ªÖn ƒê·ªó Tr&amp;uacute;c Ph∆∞∆°ng cho bi·∫øt ch·ªã ƒë&amp;atilde; nh·∫≠n quy&amp;ecirc;n g&amp;oacute;p ri&amp;ecirc;ng cho ho&amp;agrave;n c·∫£nh c·ªßa &amp;ocirc;ng Vinh v&amp;agrave; ƒë∆∞·ª£c m·∫°nh th∆∞·ªùng qu&amp;acirc;n ·ªßng h·ªô s·ªë ti·ªÅn 200 tri·ªáu ƒë·ªìng. V&amp;igrave; l&amp;agrave; s·ªë ti·ªÅn l·ªõn, ch·ªã tr&amp;iacute;ch ti·ªÅn g·ª≠i cho &amp;ocirc;ng Vinh 150 tri·ªáu ƒë·ªìng trong ƒë&amp;oacute; 120 tri·ªáu ƒë·ªìng v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;agrave;i kho·∫£n 